<h4 style="margin-top: 4pt"><a href="https://iterm2.com/downloads/beta/iTerm2-3_1_6beta1.zip"><img src="/images/Download.png" width=100 height=27 style="padding-right: 10pt">iTerm2 3.1.6beta1 (OS 10.10+)
